tr.td:
Configuring the number of lanes per port after breaking out the port is not effective. To work around this issue, first unset the breakout with the {{nv unset interface <port> breakout}} and {{nv config apply}} commands, then reconfigure the breakout and the lanes with the {{nv set interface <interface> link breakout <breakout> lanes-per-port <lanes>}} command. For example:
{{cumulus@switch:~$ nv unset interface swp1 link breakout}} 
{{cumulus@switch:~$ nv config apply}}
{{cumulus@switch:~$ nv set interface swp1 link breakout 2x lanes-per-port 2}}
{{cumulus@switch:~$ nv config apply}}
